00:22:21.590 --> 00:22:22.890
She wanted to sleep.

00:22:22.890 --> 00:22:24.070
She needed to eat.

00:22:24.070 --> 00:22:26.300
She split the difference
and looked around.

00:22:26.300 --> 00:22:29.010
Four more minutes
to go and only eight

00:22:29.010 --> 00:22:33.590
of the original 20 competitors
still stood on the line.

00:22:33.590 --> 00:22:37.060
For the first time she could see
that, just past the grits eater

00:22:37.060 --> 00:22:39.710
and a bloated man wearing
novelty sunglasses,

00:22:39.710 --> 00:22:42.500
stood Sonya Thomas,
The Black Widow.

00:22:42.500 --> 00:22:44.360
She was a svelte
Korean-born woman

00:22:44.360 --> 00:22:46.370
who had managed a Burger
King before becoming

00:22:46.370 --> 00:22:48.970
the second highest ranked
gurgitator on Earth.

00:22:48.970 --> 00:22:51.430
She held a dozen world
records and, according

00:22:51.430 --> 00:22:52.920
to the scoreboard,
a chicken wing

00:22:52.920 --> 00:22:55.630
that would put her 26
points out of reach.

00:22:55.630 --> 00:22:59.150
Charlie's stomach suddenly
felt like a much smaller place.

00:22:59.150 --> 00:23:00.720
Somewhere outside
of her body, she

00:23:00.720 --> 00:23:02.780
could see herself chewing again.

00:23:02.780 --> 00:23:05.020
She had never planned
on beating Sonya Thomas,

00:23:05.020 --> 00:23:08.000
she had only prayed
she wouldn't show up.

00:23:08.000 --> 00:23:09.830
Some people want to
kill their idols,

00:23:09.830 --> 00:23:11.980
but Charlie didn't want a fight.

00:23:11.980 --> 00:23:14.800
She just wanted to
get out of Alabama.

00:23:14.800 --> 00:23:17.470
A mechanical waltz
settled over her body.

00:23:17.470 --> 00:23:18.160
Grab.

00:23:18.160 --> 00:23:18.780
Chew.

00:23:18.780 --> 00:23:19.870
Swallow.

00:23:19.870 --> 00:23:23.190
She struggled to distract
herself from the replete pain

00:23:23.190 --> 00:23:25.440
and doubt welling
up in her guts.

00:23:25.440 --> 00:23:28.360
She thought back to home and
the perpetual motion of her life

00:23:28.360 --> 00:23:30.140
as a Podunk pariah.

00:23:30.140 --> 00:23:32.020
In the dregs of
her diffidence, she

00:23:32.020 --> 00:23:33.950
knew that she'd
fed the beast, had

00:23:33.950 --> 00:23:36.970
let the hurt go deeper
than skin and had grown

00:23:36.970 --> 00:23:40.190
fatter, weirder, even
meaner as a result.

00:23:40.190 --> 00:23:42.930
She'd craved the hard touch of a
town that would never claim her

00:23:42.930 --> 00:23:46.045
as their own, never love
her, never brag about her.

00:23:46.045 --> 00:23:49.130
Her hope had been shining
through an ever-clenching

00:23:49.130 --> 00:23:51.540
pinhole, but in
that lens she'd seen

00:23:51.540 --> 00:23:53.910
The Widow competing
on television.

00:23:53.910 --> 00:23:57.380
Charlie recognized her kindred
in strife, another misfit

00:23:57.380 --> 00:23:58.820
among rubes.

00:23:58.820 --> 00:24:02.080
She saw in Sonya Thomas a
whisper of freedom, a liberty

00:24:02.080 --> 00:24:05.320
to dance on the edge of
womanhood and thrive.

00:24:05.320 --> 00:24:09.030
Charlie's training had started
the spring she turned 17.

00:24:09.030 --> 00:24:11.780
Her parents met her intentions
of becoming a major league

00:24:11.780 --> 00:24:14.820
eater with a skepticism
bordering hostility.

00:24:14.820 --> 00:24:17.460
17 years of
semi-responsible parenting

00:24:17.460 --> 00:24:20.080
had severely moderated
the Eaglehorne idea

00:24:20.080 --> 00:24:22.130
of acceptable life-goals.

00:24:22.130 --> 00:24:24.610
Really, they worried that
their chronically unpopular

00:24:24.610 --> 00:24:27.450
daughter's plan to etch a living
shoving food down her throat

00:24:27.450 --> 00:24:29.700
was a proposition in suicide.

00:24:29.700 --> 00:24:31.840
She'd had to declare
the discussion ended

00:24:31.840 --> 00:24:33.340
more than once.

00:24:33.340 --> 00:24:36.020
In fact, she'd never
been further from death.

00:24:36.020 --> 00:24:38.150
Her regimen was
modeled on what she

00:24:38.150 --> 00:24:40.360
could glean from her
idol's sporadic television

00:24:40.360 --> 00:24:42.340
appearances and the internet.

00:24:42.340 --> 00:24:44.970
It was surprisingly in step
with the recommendations

00:24:44.970 --> 00:24:46.410
of modern medicine.

00:24:46.410 --> 00:24:50.540
Eight hours of sleep at night,
daily jogs, and a strict 1700

00:24:50.540 --> 00:24:53.590
calorie diet filled with
fruits and vegetables.

00:24:53.590 --> 00:24:56.910
Of course, eating all that food
at once isn't in many fitness

00:24:56.910 --> 00:24:59.860
manuals, to say nothing of
her biweekly all-you-can-eat

00:24:59.860 --> 00:25:03.220
'workouts,' but the overall
improvement in Charlie's health

00:25:03.220 --> 00:25:04.620
was undeniable.

00:25:04.620 --> 00:25:06.980
By the fall, she'd
lost 78 pounds

00:25:06.980 --> 00:25:08.720
and gained the
beauty and confidence

00:25:08.720 --> 00:25:13.160
of a girl who truly believes
she has control over food.

00:25:13.160 --> 00:25:15.500
Her public enthusiasm
of eating competitions

00:25:15.500 --> 00:25:17.600
did her few favors
with her peers,

00:25:17.600 --> 00:25:19.500
but her reclaimed
featherweight kilter

00:25:19.500 --> 00:25:21.170
and the off-brand
hormones her father

00:25:21.170 --> 00:25:24.690
bought online had given her
a peculiar prettiness that

00:25:24.690 --> 00:25:27.690
at least kept boys from
throwing rocks at her.

00:25:27.690 --> 00:25:29.930
Her friendship remained
a social pitfall

00:25:29.930 --> 00:25:32.890
Lulu alone was willing to risk.

00:25:32.890 --> 00:25:35.050
With 30 seconds
left, something was

00:25:35.050 --> 00:25:37.270
very wrong and getting worse.

00:25:37.270 --> 00:25:40.210
The 83 wings she'd
somehow swallowed

00:25:40.210 --> 00:25:42.450
were now in open revolt.

00:25:42.450 --> 00:25:45.240
Terror tied a knot in her
stomach, making her nausea

00:25:45.240 --> 00:25:47.170
feel all the more urgent.

00:25:47.170 --> 00:25:49.100
She'd eaten beyond her means.

00:25:49.100 --> 00:25:51.980
Charlie was going to throw up.

00:25:51.980 --> 00:25:54.120
Her breath came
in shallow gulps.

00:25:54.120 --> 00:25:56.960
She wobbled drunkenly as
her strength began to break

00:25:56.960 --> 00:25:58.680
and she closed her eyes.

00:25:58.680 --> 00:26:01.100
Clammy certainty enveloped her.

00:26:01.100 --> 00:26:03.800
Vomiting was intractable
and inevitable,

00:26:03.800 --> 00:26:06.370
but desperately
needed to be stalled.

00:26:06.370 --> 00:26:08.930
If a drop of her sick
touched the table

00:26:08.930 --> 00:26:12.490
before the clock ran out,
she'd be disqualified.

00:26:12.490 --> 00:26:14.590
A great wave of
adrenaline washed up

00:26:14.590 --> 00:26:17.960
the last bit of resolve
she'd so jealously buried.

00:26:17.960 --> 00:26:21.030
It was immediately followed
by the half-digested ambitions

00:26:21.030 --> 00:26:23.080
at the back of her throat.

00:26:23.080 --> 00:26:25.440
Charlie's hands
shot to her mouth.

00:26:25.440 --> 00:26:28.280
A gleeful explosion
of pleasure roared out

00:26:28.280 --> 00:26:30.260
of the voyeuristic crowd.

00:26:30.260 --> 00:26:31.970
Her shoulders heaved
as though she'd

00:26:31.970 --> 00:26:35.090
been shoved by an invisible
hand and she teetered slightly

00:26:35.090 --> 00:26:36.160
forward.

00:26:36.160 --> 00:26:39.360
The drool in her mouth
tasted like batteries.

00:26:39.360 --> 00:26:42.230
The mess in her guts came
flooding out over her lips

00:26:42.230 --> 00:26:44.240
and into her waiting palms.

00:26:44.240 --> 00:26:48.060
She shuddered violently as
she buckled and began to fall.

00:26:48.060 --> 00:26:51.200
The final buzzer screamed
out over the chaos.

00:26:51.200 --> 00:26:52.980
The Championship was over.

00:26:52.980 --> 00:26:55.290
Charlie's world
strobed into blackness

00:26:55.290 --> 00:26:57.640
and she collapsed
unconscious into a pile

00:26:57.640 --> 00:27:00.020
of puke and victory.

00:27:00.020 --> 00:27:04.070
In her hallucinations, Charlie
watched the Big Bang spew forth

00:27:04.070 --> 00:27:06.090
and begin to eat itself.

00:27:06.090 --> 00:27:09.580
She perceived a cycle of
consumption, the tidal glut

00:27:09.580 --> 00:27:13.560
of energy that crushes stars
and digests the cosmos.

00:27:13.560 --> 00:27:17.450
At the center of each galaxy
sat an endlessly hungry mouth,

00:27:17.450 --> 00:27:20.170
a black hole that bolted
down creation and waited

00:27:20.170 --> 00:27:23.210
for the final
buzzer of doomsday.

00:27:23.210 --> 00:27:25.320
Serenely, she
recognized creation

00:27:25.320 --> 00:27:27.710
as an elaborate eating contest.

00:27:27.710 --> 00:27:30.090
The thought made her happy.

00:27:30.090 --> 00:27:33.920
She woke up to the bright white
glow of tarp in the sunshine.

00:27:33.920 --> 00:27:36.340
Her head lay on a
starched, sterile pillow,

00:27:36.340 --> 00:27:38.580
and a clear tube
of saline dripped

00:27:38.580 --> 00:27:40.990
into a vein in the
crook of her elbow.

00:27:40.990 --> 00:27:43.660
The ebullient bustle of
post-competition commotion

00:27:43.660 --> 00:27:46.280
outside told her that she'd
been unconscious for only

00:27:46.280 --> 00:27:49.870
a few minutes, though she felt
like she'd witnessed eternity.

00:27:49.870 --> 00:27:51.680
Sitting up drew the
relieved attention

00:27:51.680 --> 00:27:54.720
of a kind-faced young medic
on the other side of the tent.

00:27:54.720 --> 00:27:56.890
Her heart fluttered,
her head throbbed,

00:27:56.890 --> 00:27:59.290
and he urged her
to lie back down.

00:27:59.290 --> 00:28:01.140
She'd almost died.

00:28:01.140 --> 00:28:03.170
It was time to rest.

00:28:03.170 --> 00:28:06.300
In a photo finish, Charlie's
vomit had stayed in her hands

00:28:06.300 --> 00:28:09.300
and off the table
until after the buzzer.

00:28:09.300 --> 00:28:11.740
The rules were clear--
she'd officially

00:28:11.740 --> 00:28:13.590
finished successfully.

00:28:13.590 --> 00:28:17.070
Charlie was awarded third
place, just five wings shy

00:28:17.070 --> 00:28:18.700
of the grits guy.

00:28:18.700 --> 00:28:20.880
On the plastic stool
next to her cot,

00:28:20.880 --> 00:28:24.110
paper-clipped to a $500 check
and a handful of Hooters

00:28:24.110 --> 00:28:27.050
coupons, was a business
card with the International

00:28:27.050 --> 00:28:29.870
Federation of Competitive
Eaters logo on it.

00:28:29.870 --> 00:28:33.620
She grinned deliriously,
belched, and fell asleep."

00:28:33.620 --> 00:28:34.790
